name: mpc-local-node2-testnet-tee
docker_compose_file:
version: '3.8'

services:
  launcher:
    image: nearone/mpc-launcher@sha256:296da33b9336ffcb31503a6640e827bca785025225f7bbc16e7b632a7ab26cfb

    container_name: launcher

    environment:
      - PLATFORM=TEE
      - DOCKER_CONTENT_TRUST=1
      - DEFAULT_IMAGE_DIGEST=sha256:07bba7c60565750f6d5fe6800cd73513dd2d0d02e6893184064e209ff37c25a2

    volumes:
      - /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock
      - /var/run/dstack.sock:/var/run/dstack.sock
      - /tapp:/tapp:ro
      - shared-volume:/mnt/shared:ro

    security_opt:
      - no-new-privileges:true

    read_only: true

    tmpfs:
      - /tmp

volumes:
  shared-volume:
    name: shared-volume
